massim.framework

Interface SimulationConfiguration

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    SimpleSimulationConfiguration
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultSimpleSimulationConfiguration, GraphSimulationConfiguration, GraphSimulationConfiguration, GraphSimulationConfiguration, GridSimulationConfiguration, GridSimulationConfiguration, GridSimulationConfiguration, GridSimulationConfiguration, GridSimulationConfiguration, GridSimulationConfigurationHandCrafted, GridSimulationConfigurationHandCrafted, GridSimulationConfigurationHandCrafted, GridSimulationConfigurationHandCrafted, GridSimulationConfigurationHandCrafted, SimulationConfigurationHandCrafted, SimulationConfigurationImpl

    public interface SimulationConfiguration
    This interface must be implemented by all classes that serve as simulation configuration. It's main purpose is to have type safety. Apart from that it is imperative that any class that implements this interface is serializable.
